
********Terminal ****************************************************
To run a test file in debug mode -
npx playwright test tests/WebAPIPart2.spec.js --debug

Run a test using specific config file - 
 -- config playwright.config.js

To auto generate playwright code which tracking manual actions -
npx playwright codegen http://www.google.com

To open an UI test runner - 
npx playwright test --ui

Run API debug -
Create a breakpoint, at the top, run "> Debug: Debug npm script"

To generate allure test result report
npx playwright test --reporter='line,allure-playwright'
allure generate ./allure-results -o ./allure-report
allure open ./allure-report